99360bafd08c54470ed8f437ba9e49c2a08671e2ac0134c64ddc08c23e6217681b97c2d7408bfcdfacd6c1e8d02d60b2726bb313421ad8935fe1cbb5937aaba4  Allow-nullable-head-parameter-in-stash_if_needed.patch"
